(2, 'Practice Makes Perfect: Basic French, Premium Second Edition', 'https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/515Ay4ui3IL._SX389_BO1,204,203,200_.jpg', 'French', 'Beginner', 'Textbook', 4, 'https://www.amazon.com/Practice-Makes-Perfect-French-Premium/dp/1259836398/ref=asc_df_1259836398/?tag=hyprod-20&linkCode=df0&hvadid=241995309321&hvpos=&hvnetw=g&hvrand=3145720493198348420&hvpone=&hvptwo=&hvqmt=&hvdev=c&hvdvcmdl=&hvlocint=&hvlocphy=9019546&hvtargid=pla-431859876365&psc=1', 'Paid', 'Practice Makes Perfect: Basic French is the proven companion to your French-learning experience. In each bite-sized lesson, author Eliane Kurbegov explains one―and only one―grammar concept and illustrates it with clear examples. These lessons are purposefully short, so you can complete them in twenty minutes or less, and go at a pace that works for you.'),
