(3, 'Advanced Spanish Grammar', 'https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/51LFLuo2bfL._SX404_BO1,204,203,200_.jpg', 'Spanish', 'Advanced', 'Textbook', 5, 'https://www.amazon.com/Advanced-Spanish-Grammar-Self-Teaching-Second/dp/0471134481?tag=fluentu-20', 'Paid', 'This complete, accessible guide clarifies grammatical structure and explains vocabulary usage to help you master Spanish. Whether you need extra help for a course, want a quick review for a test, or simply want to brush up your language skills, this is the book to have.'),
